      "rationale": "At MRL 2, level 1 for numerical solver error is acceptable without formal iterative error quantification beyond residual monitoring. Residuals converged to 1e-6 for all equations. Round-off error deemed negligible for double-precision solver. Not formally assessed per MRL 2 scoping agreement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
