      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented simulation plan and peer review of setup sufficient at level 1 for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Simulation plan reviewed by independent CFD engineer prior to execution. Boundary condition setup cross-checked against experimental protocol. No formal use-error audit required at MRL 2 level 1. Not formally assessed per MRL 2 scoping agreement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification of turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model selection required at level 1 for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature for rotating blood pump flows. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) applied consistently with prior FDA benchmark studies. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2 level 1. Not formally assessed per MRL 2 scoping agreement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
