      "rationale": "Blood analog viscosity and density measured at 37°C and documented in test report. Pump geometry nominal dimensions from CAD model; manufacturing tolerances ±0.05 mm documented. Sensitivity of hemolysis index to input variation not formally quantified at MRL 2 level 1. Not formally assessed per MRL 2 scoping agreement."
