    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all 5 operating points. Package conforms to ProfileMinimal; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be appended prior to regulatory submission.",
